stylometry: RISKSIMTABLE allows you to run the same simulation with multipule order quantities. This model would be use when a car dealership is tring to determine how many cars to order, when they want to maximize their profits. In this model there would be a range of quantities to order and the model in turn would show the mean and the standard deviation for each of the order quantities, allowing ht edealrship to select the right amount of cars for them to order to maximize their profits. It alows them to see that they may have an option that could have a high profit but the risk of that option might be higher than an option with a lower profit.  RSIKSIMTABLE allows you to see the risk associated with multipule order quantities.
